This Privacy Policy describes how [Your Company Name] ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares information when you use the IBWS (Interface Between Warehouse and Store) Android application ("the App").

By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

1. Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information
The App may collect the following personal information for authentication and operational purposes:

User name

Email address

Phone number

Warehouse/store identification details

1.2 Non-Personal Information
We may collect non-personal data, including:

Device information (model, OS version)

Log data (app usage, errors, and performance metrics)

IP address (for security purposes)

1.3 Data Related to Warehouse & Store Operations
The App may process:

Inventory details

Order transactions

Shipping and receiving logs

Employee activity logs

2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected data for:

User authentication and account management

Facilitating communication between warehouses and stores

Improving app functionality and performance

Ensuring security and preventing fraud

Generating reports for business operations

3. Data Sharing & Disclosure
We do not sell your personal data. However, we may share information with:

Authorized employees (for operational purposes)

Third-party service providers (e.g., cloud storage, analytics)

Legal authorities (if required by law)

4. Data Security
We implement security measures to protect your data, including:

Encryption for sensitive data

Secure authentication protocols

Regular security audits

5. Data Retention
We retain user data only as long as necessary for business operations or as required by law.

6. Your Rights
Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:

Access, correct, or delete your data

Restrict or object to data processing

Request data portability

To exercise these rights, contact us at [Your Contact Email].

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Users will be notified of significant changes.

